messages.author: Mustafa
messages.text:
Portrait of Vincent van Gogh by John Peter Russell.

"The Australian painter John Peter Russell got to know Vincent at Fernand Cormons studio. He painted this portrait of his friend in 1886 in a conventional, realistic style. It is clearly influenced by photography, although the face and the hand still show Impressionist touches."

text_entities.text:
Portrait of Vincent van Gogh by John Peter Russell.

"The Australian painter John Peter Russell got to know Vincent at Fernand Cormons studio. He painted this portrait of his friend in 1886 in a conventional, realistic style. It is clearly influenced by photography, although the face and the hand still show Impressionist touches."
